caller_intent: The caller wants to initiate an insurance claim after hitting a deer with a company vehicle and attempted to contact someone else without success.
resolution_steps: Agent asked whether the vehicle involved was personal or commercial.
Caller confirmed it was a company vehicle.
Agent requested a moment to process the information.
knowledge_required: Claims process for commercial vehicle accidents
summary: A caller attempted to start a commercial vehicle insurance claim after hitting a deer. The agent asked clarifying questions about the vehicle type and temporarily paused the call to process the request. The conversation was cut off before resolution, requiring a follow-up.
